            . I live in Great Queen-street, Lincoln's-inn, and am a coach-painter. I was in <placeName id="t18310630-143-crimeloc767">Newgate-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310630-143-crimeloc767" type="placeName" value="Newgate-street"></interp>
