                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-143-off765 t18310630-143-crimeloc767"></join>; I saw my handkerchief on the ground, and took it up - this is it; a man was pursued and taken, but I cannot say whether it was the prisoner; I have inquired, and find the prisoner had had a good character before, and he has been a great support to his parents.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received an excellent character.</p>
